CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 7, 1958, pg. A3, reads: "Last Drink - Member from far and near gave Loendi a gay and festive air over the week-end, reminiscent of its halcyon days, as "spirits" flowed freely."
TitMainTitle: Men, and women, including one wearing light colored suit, gathered behind bar with bottles in glasses, in Loendi Club, with sign for Carling's Red Cap Ale in background
